WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.531 --> 00:00:01.766
Good morning, family.

00:00:01.766 --> 00:00:03.285
How are y'all doing?

00:00:03.285 --> 00:00:05.532
I have some things on my heart today.

00:00:06.293 --> 00:00:26.963
After I made that last video, I got a ton of emails from everybody.

00:00:26.963 --> 00:01:15.480
Some of the emails were rude and some were kind, but I received a really good email that really blessed me.

00:01:15.480 --> 00:01:35.143
I'm going to have my wife read this to you.

00:01:35.143 --> 00:02:22.954
It's a prophecy about a visitation from the Lord back in 2015 that explains everything about what happened and why the judgment was set and why it didn't happen.

00:02:22.954 --> 00:03:37.950
Whenever I told you all that I had these warnings from the Holy Spirit in 2013 and 2014, the Lord warned me that there was going to be a major storm—basically the beginning of all heck breaking loose upon the world with the Shmita cycle.

00:03:37.950 --> 00:04:57.062
Rabbi Jonathan Cahn wrote the book 'The Harbinger,' and there were so many prophetic voices saying something was going to happen, but I was never really able to get a word from the Lord about what happened when something didn't happen.

00:05:02.791 --> 00:05:32.120
I understand the power of prayer and the authority God has called us to exercise on this earth.

00:05:35.885 --> 00:06:04.971
When he came to me and said, 'Brandon, things have changed,' he gave us more grace and time.

00:06:04.971 --> 00:06:18.262
That was back in August of 2015.

00:06:32.691 --> 00:06:42.199
To whoever sent this to me, I won't say your name, but I want to say thank you.

00:06:42.199 --> 00:06:51.708
This really blessed me today.

00:06:52.697 --> 00:07:17.980
I don't know the man who had this visitation, but I believe he is legitimate.

00:07:17.980 --> 00:07:59.713
He sees things the way I have seen them throughout my life of visitations, and the way he describes the angels is absolutely amazing.

00:07:59.713 --> 00:08:11.986
Please listen to the whole thing.

00:08:11.986 --> 00:08:49.200
My wife is going to read this now, and I'll be back afterward to pray for you.

00:08:49.200 --> 00:08:52.990
'Hi everybody.

00:08:52.990 --> 00:08:57.307
I'm Brandon's wife.

00:08:57.307 --> 00:09:06.640
It's so good to be here.

00:09:06.640 --> 00:09:17.964
We love and appreciate you all.

00:09:17.964 --> 00:09:50.409
I will now read this vision from the email: I had a vision as I was eating lunch recently.

00:09:50.409 --> 00:11:08.640
Suddenly, a portal opened in the spirit realm, and my angel said to me, "You are summoned to the courtroom of Heaven to record the case being tried now, so that God's people will know the lateness of the hour.

00:11:08.640 --> 00:11:34.540
You must warn them so that the bride may awaken and take heed.

00:11:35.000 --> 00:11:42.120
The time is short.

00:11:42.120 --> 00:12:03.455
" I was escorted by two angels to the Supreme courtroom.

00:12:03.455 --> 00:12:24.023
There were many hundreds of angels and saints already seated.

00:12:24.023 --> 00:12:49.331
It looked like a giant arena with thousands of seats.

00:12:52.600 --> 00:13:16.253
There were five big leather chairs with gold embossed cards that said "recorder.

00:13:30.787 --> 00:13:36.370
" I was ushered into the one closest to the bench.

00:13:36.370 --> 00:14:09.327
I was handed a feather quill and a parchment scroll that worked like an iPad.

00:14:16.445 --> 00:14:43.580
The angel said, "You are one of five prophet recorders summoned from the Earth to witness this trial.

00:14:43.580 --> 00:15:15.371
" I recognized one of the others as a current prophet on Earth from the Western world.

00:15:15.371 --> 00:15:42.600
Another was a lady from Africa, and the fifth was a man from America.

00:15:47.423 --> 00:15:57.497
I was given a yarmulke of golden color.

00:15:57.497 --> 00:16:30.249
An angel who presided over the courtroom named Justice stood up; she was about 20 feet tall.

00:16:30.249 --> 00:16:44.131
Then the angel Justice shouted, "All rise!

00:16:49.640 --> 00:17:11.600
The Honorable Ancient of Days, the judge of all creation, is present and presiding.

00:17:11.600 --> 00:17:24.487
" We all stood in unison.

00:17:24.487 --> 00:17:42.909
I saw the throne clothed in white blinding light.

00:17:43.331 --> 00:18:46.679
The other judges were Enoch, Father Abraham, Moses, David, Elijah, and Daniel on the Father's right; on his left were John the Baptist, Peter, James, John, Andrew, and Paul the Apostle.

00:18:49.675 --> 00:19:03.910
Then the case was read by Lady Justice.

00:19:03.910 --> 00:19:36.137
She spoke: "The timing of the final judgments of the Day of the Lord must be decided.

00:19:41.591 --> 00:20:20.760
The accuser, Satan, is prosecuting, declaring that Adam's lease is over and he must be allowed to take ownership of the Earth.

00:20:20.760 --> 00:20:43.067
" Representing the holy defense was the Lord Yeshua, Jesus the Messiah.

00:20:43.067 --> 00:21:08.839
Satan was a handsome man who sat stone-faced at the prosecution table.

00:21:08.839 --> 00:21:57.639
He began his long diatribe of accusation against fallen man, demanding control of the Earth for seven years through the son of perdition.

00:21:57.639 --> 00:22:36.799
Yeshua then arose and said, "As the true Son of Man, I have taken the death penalty for every generation.

00:22:36.799 --> 00:23:25.159
Through the intercession of my holy bride on Earth, there has been granted a pause to allow for the fullness of the harvest.

00:23:25.159 --> 00:23:41.679
" Satan, or HaSatan, was busy reading the scroll feverishly.

00:23:41.679 --> 00:24:16.840
The defense petitioned the court for another extension of time in the grace purchased by the blood on the cross.

00:24:16.840 --> 00:24:47.052
After some deliberation, every judge voted in favor of the saints to extend another period of grace.

00:24:56.240 --> 00:25:18.520
The Father spoke: "I decree that the prosecution has failed to bring a closing to the final days of grace.

00:25:18.520 --> 00:25:42.039
However, the birthing pains and judgments on the earth will not be stopped.

00:25:42.039 --> 00:25:59.740
HaSatan has the authority to rule over the tares of the earth.

00:25:59.740 --> 00:26:32.744
Those that do not abide with me in the secret place are in more peril with each passing day.

00:26:32.744 --> 00:26:53.000
The time of grace is nearly over.

00:27:02.394 --> 00:27:02.729
This is the midnight hour.

00:27:02.729 --> 00:27:20.804
" Then Lady Justice raised a scale.

00:27:20.804 --> 00:27:51.960
An angel poured black sand from a brass urn, representing the accumulated sin of mankind.

00:27:51.960 --> 00:28:23.217
Another angel poured white sand from a white urn representing the prayers and intercession of the overcoming church.

00:28:24.111 --> 00:28:39.439
The scale shifted as the white bowl went down.

00:28:47.360 --> 00:29:13.960
The Father said, "The time of grace shall be extended for a little longer to finish the final harvest.

00:29:21.400 --> 00:29:32.382
" I then signed the recording scroll and the vision ended.

00:29:32.382 --> 00:29:57.025
' Dearly beloved bride of Messiah, we must labor now while it is light.

00:30:06.593 --> 00:30:07.067
People, get ready.

00:30:25.011 --> 00:30:25.234
Jesus is coming.

00:30:26.905 --> 00:30:36.840
Well, what did y'all think about that?

00:30:36.840 --> 00:30:48.380
I've been in that courtroom in the spirit.

00:30:48.380 --> 00:31:33.590
I've seen Satan as the accuser of the brethren, and I saw that the blood of Jesus Christ spoke for me.

00:31:33.590 --> 00:31:40.919
It's amazing that someone else had such a detailed vision that aligns with what I've seen.

00:31:55.840 --> 00:31:58.749
The Lord keeps granting more time through our prayers.

00:31:58.749 --> 00:32:20.902
I want to teach you your authority and intercession to avert certain things.

00:32:20.902 --> 00:32:43.225
I believe we can change the outcome of many events through prayer and obedience.

00:32:43.225 --> 00:33:17.253
My tallit is what I use when I stand in the gap for America.

00:33:28.154 --> 00:33:38.428
The birthing pains are not going to stop; they're going to increase.

00:33:39.800 --> 00:33:58.000
The light of the Father is brighter than the noonday sun.

00:33:58.000 --> 00:34:10.247
We are about to see a billion-soul harvest.

00:34:10.247 --> 00:34:37.022
Please like this video and subscribe to our channel; it helps the algorithm spread the gospel.

00:34:37.022 --> 00:34:44.726
Let me pray for you.

00:34:44.726 --> 00:35:01.498
Father, I thank you for every person here.

00:35:03.630 --> 00:35:24.800
I call for Holy Ghost boldness and fire to come down upon them.

00:35:33.210 --> 00:35:46.555
I speak to the spirit of fear and command it to release them.

00:35:46.555 --> 00:35:53.754
I cover you with the blood and thank you, Lord, that the light that pierces all darkness is shining on you.

00:35:53.754 --> 00:36:09.884
We thank you for creative ideas for soul-winning.

00:36:19.839 --> 00:36:31.900
We thank you that we have a better covenant through Jesus Christ.

00:36:31.900 --> 00:36:41.279
In Jesus' name, amen.

00:36:41.279 --> 00:37:00.915
Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:37:00.915 --> 00:37:17.880
Jesus loves you, and we will see you next time.

00:37:17.880 --> 00:37:19.800
Bye-bye.
